{"tid":662036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係日本]JR西日本一列新快速列車早開25秒，鐵路公司致歉","createTime":"2018-05-12T05:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T08:21:35.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a77e6a516f3a09edfe2956f71ff5c16839da1ab3","tid":662036,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.asahi.com/sp/articles/ASL5C4GXWL5CPTIL00V.html?iref=sptop_8_06\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Fsp%2Farticles%2FASL5C4GXWL5CPTIL00V.html%3Firef%3Dsptop_8_06&d=0GBvpCFIhN75uPy7XBKWkQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=2f63857a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asahi.com/sp/articles/ASL5C4GXWL5CPTIL00V.html?iref=sptop_8_06</a><br />\n<br />\nＪＲ西日本は１１日、琵琶湖線の能登川駅（滋賀県東近江市）で、同日午前７時１２分発の西明石行き新快速電車（１２両）が２５秒早く発車したと発表した。数人が乗れなかったという。<br />\n<br />\n　ＪＲ西によると、車掌は、発車の定刻を同１１分と勘違いしてドアを閉めた後、１分早いと気づいたが、ホームに客の姿が見えないのを確認して出発したと説明したという。しかし実際はホームに客数人が取り残され、「定刻より早く出発した」と男性客１人から連絡を受けた駅員が謝罪したという。ＪＲ西は「お客様に大変迷惑をかけた。基本動作を徹底し、再発防止に努める」としている。"},{"pid":"8db9677079a2dbc66390ba7614b0725c08bf8dd3","tid":662036,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2315ae3811295db33dafc8ff0d95e784b3d4b465","tid":662036,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"廢鐵就...無謂講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f716e26bd829abb303c9789bec430ca02970d2e","tid":662036,"uid":136467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"香港: 遲咗幾個鐘都係同你講信號故障係好正常既事"},{"pid":"4aa58dd13618b0ce4d64b72ecd45c43f65f2334f","tid":662036,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑：龜鐵叻過日本，永遠唔會早開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n